                     <interp inst="t18171203-23-off136" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18171203-23-cd137" type="crimeDate">6th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-23-off136 t18171203-23-cd137"></join>, one bag, value 2d., and fifty-six pounds of rice, value 18s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18171203-23-victim232" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Shillcock
                        <interp inst="t18171203-23-victim232" type="surname" value="Shillcock"></interp>
